==International adaptations==
An [[Australia]]n version of the format, ''[[Best Bits (Australian TV series)|Best Bits]]'', will air from 29 March 2016 on the [[Seven Network]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2016/03/airdate-best-bits.html|title=Airdate:Best Bits |date=21 March 2016|accessdate=21 March 2016|first=David|last=Knox|work=[[TV Tonight]]}}</ref>

